    "is_free": false,
    "description": "你需要扮演奇娅，从残酷的残酷暴君Meavora手中拯救自己的父亲；沿路对抗Meavora创造的布条士兵，利用你独特的能力——变身或控制身边的动物和物体。攀爬也好，滑翔也罢，在这些绝美的海洋岛屿间探索冒险；在这里，你还将结识很多新朋友，了解他们的奇妙生活，发展你们的奇遇。这片美丽的景色，灵感来源于新喀里多尼亚；这游戏里的故事，灵感来源于一段诗意的成长时光。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >灵魂出窍</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/62ee7db569d36d4ec8184338b332f0be.poster.avif?t=1727258805\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/62ee7db569d36d4ec8184338b332f0be.webm?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/62ee7db569d36d4ec8184338b332f0be.mp4?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Tchia将能够凭借自身的独特天赋操控周遭的动物或者是物体。超过30种动物与百余种物体供你选择，化身飞鸟翱翔天际、变成鱼儿探索大海、或者是差遣狗狗挖掘宝藏！利用独特的灵魂出窍能力破解谜题，发掘岛上的秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索&amp;游历</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/66ffce7073d614c78e457e907fdcea9d.poster.avif?t=1727258805\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/66ffce7073d614c78e457e907fdcea9d.webm?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/66ffce7073d614c78e457e907fdcea9d.mp4?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>跳跃和滑翔能帮助你在群岛间完成穿梭；但记得入水时刻保持优雅，更低的水花姿势更美。攀爬的快乐，在树顶遥看夕阳时，你便会懂得。在珊瑚礁或沉船周围潜水时要小心了，海浪很美，时间也会过得特别快。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗&amp;遭遇</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/b604cbacabcbc7690b6573e42981ef12.poster.avif?t=1727258805\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/b604cbacabcbc7690b6573e42981ef12.webm?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/b604cbacabcbc7690b6573e42981ef12.mp4?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>勇敢面对暴君Meavora，Ta不过是木块和布条组成的“纸老虎”罢了。随机应变，你的奇特天赋只需克服紧张，正常发挥就足够解决这些战斗。如果想挑战技能极限，试试神秘挑战吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尤克里里</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/910cac77a13dface96e8ab70a9e3ba1e.poster.avif?t=1727258805\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/910cac77a13dface96e8ab70a9e3ba1e.webm?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/910cac77a13dface96e8ab70a9e3ba1e.mp4?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>尤克里里将一直陪伴着你；夕阳下独奏一曲小调，或是与岛民在篝火旁合奏，都是很棒的选择。尤克里里也是探索之旅的关键钥匙，用Ta去完成一系列特殊动作，推动冒险成长故事吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事&amp;音乐</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/fb765caa76eb47655d3f71065a84371d.poster.avif?t=1727258805\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/fb765caa76eb47655d3f71065a84371d.webm?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/fb765caa76eb47655d3f71065a84371d.mp4?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏灵感来源于新喀里多尼亚当地文化。原汁原味的当地语言配音，精致的过场动画，自然声音采样的原创管弦乐曲，这一切只为尽可能与你还原那一片美丽又独特的海岛。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定制外观&amp;物品</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/0efaaf55700f8d6f10fc1cd27d94f8e1.poster.avif?t=1727258805\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/0efaaf55700f8d6f10fc1cd27d94f8e1.webm?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/0efaaf55700f8d6f10fc1cd27d94f8e1.mp4?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>使用数百种可解锁道具，装点你的服饰与小船，从传统风格到华丽浮夸应有尽有。除此以外，你还将在冒险途中解锁手电筒、弹弓、指南针、照相机等等各式各样好玩又有用的工具。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新喀里多尼亚</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/976be983cab1d4160ea1e26336023982.poster.avif?t=1727258805\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/976be983cab1d4160ea1e26336023982.webm?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1496590/extras/976be983cab1d4160ea1e26336023982.mp4?t=1727258805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《奇娅 Tchia》游戏中的一切，都取材于新喀里多尼亚，这座漂泊于太平洋上的一隅小岛同时也是Awaceb各位创始人们的家园。当地丰富多样的风土人情、文化、音乐、语言、民俗与传统之间的融合碰撞，为游戏带来了与众不同的表现力；新喀里多尼亚当地的艺术家们以当地传统语言为我们带来了活灵活现的角色配音，希望《奇娅 Tchia》能为你带来一段或轻松或奇妙的海岛冒险体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想要在《奇娅 Tchia》的群岛中享受更多的悠然时光吗？</h2>《奇娅 Tchia》的免费更新包含8首灵魂歌曲，让你能在探索时享受更多的乐趣，像是特技模式、火焰能力或是快艇！你还可以装备各种不同的新服装，且所有外观道具现在都会为你的旅程提供额外特殊效果，像是更多体力或特殊技能。所以想要组建自己的螃蟹战队或是吸引鲨鱼的话，那就快穿上不同服装吧！",
